# Danh sch cc truy vn cn thc hin
queries = [
    # Thm kha chnh (PRIMARY KEY) cho tng bng
    "ALTER TABLE fact_voucher ADD PRIMARY KEY (voucher_id);",
    "ALTER TABLE dim_order ADD PRIMARY KEY (order_id);",
    "ALTER TABLE dim_client ADD PRIMARY KEY (client_id);",
    "ALTER TABLE dim_brand ADD PRIMARY KEY (brand_id);",
    "ALTER TABLE dim_category ADD PRIMARY KEY (category_id);",
    "ALTER TABLE dim_voucher_status ADD PRIMARY KEY (status_id);",

    # Thm kha ngoi (FOREIGN KEY) vo bng fact_voucher
    "ALTER TABLE fact_voucher ADD CONSTRAINT fk_fact_voucher_client FOREIGN KEY (client_id) REFERENCES dim_client(client_id);",
    "ALTER TABLE fact_voucher ADD CONSTRAINT fk_fact_voucher_order FOREIGN KEY (order_id) REFERENCES dim_order(order_id);",
    "ALTER TABLE fact_voucher ADD CONSTRAINT fk_fact_voucher_status FOREIGN KEY (voucher_status_id) REFERENCES dim_voucher_status(status_id);",
    "ALTER TABLE fact_voucher ADD CONSTRAINT fk_fact_voucher_brand FOREIGN KEY (used_brand_id) REFERENCES dim_brand(brand_id);",

    # Thm kha ngoi cho bng dim_brand
    "ALTER TABLE dim_brand ADD CONSTRAINT fk_dim_brand_category FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES dim_category(category_id);",

    # To View  kt hp d liu cc bng
    """
    CREATE VIEW brand_category_info AS
    SELECT 
        b.brand_id,
        b.active,
        b.type,
        b.category_id,
        c.name_ci AS category_name_ci,
        c.name_en AS category_name_en
    FROM dim_brand b
    JOIN dim_category c ON b.category_id = c.category_id;
    """,
    """
    CREATE VIEW unified_data AS
    SELECT 
        f.voucher_id,
        f.created_date,
        f.client_id,
        c.name AS client_name,
        c.created_date AS client_created_date,
        c.active AS client_active,
        c.client_size,
        c.client_sector,
        c.client_type,
        c.client_location,
        f.order_id,
        o.order_type,
        f.voucher_type,
        f.voucher_link,
        f.voucher_status_id,
        s.status AS voucher_status,
        f.used_date,
        f.used_brand_id,
        bc.active AS brand_active,
        bc.type AS brand_type,
        bc.category_id,
        bc.category_name_ci,
        bc.category_name_en,
        f.expired_date,
        f.value
    FROM fact_voucher f
    JOIN dim_client c ON f.client_id = c.client_id
    JOIN dim_order o ON f.order_id = o.order_id
    JOIN dim_voucher_status s ON f.voucher_status_id = s.status_id
    LEFT JOIN brand_category_info bc ON f.used_brand_id = bc.brand_id;
    """
]

# Thc hin tng truy vn
with engine.connect() as connection:
    for query in queries:
        try:
            connection.execute(query)
        except Exception as e:
            print(f"Li khi thc hin truy vn: {query}\n{e}\n")

Dashboard with PowerBI

Loi hnh kinh doanh mua bn voucher nh ca Got It mang li nhiu li ch cho c doanh nghip v ngi tiu dng. i vi doanh nghip, vic pht hnh voucher gip thc y doanh s bn hng, qung b thng hiu v thu ht khch hng mi. i vi ngi tiu dng, voucher mang li s linh hot trong mua sm, tit kim chi ph v c hi tri nghim a dng sn phm, dch v t nhiu thng hiu khc nhau.

Da trn d liu cung cp v tnh hnh hot ng kinh doanh voucher t 01/2022 - n thi im hin ti vi cc voucher c cung cp n ht nm 2024. Trong khong thi gian ny, doanh doanh thu ht khong hn 92 nghn order ng vi 92K loi voucher tng gi tr voucher pht hnh khong gn 14 t VND, bao gm:

  • Cc voucher c s dng chim phn ln nht, tip theo l cc voucher qu hn s dng v mt s voucher b cancelled, inactive hay not counted chim khong 8K (9%) tng s lng order.
  • Cc order c to th cong bi ADMIN chim phn ln, tip theo l API
  • Qua cc nm hot ng, du hiu rt tch cc l s lng order voucher t cc oanh nghip client tng ln, c bit l thi im 2022-2023 tc d tng trng 100%, tip tc duy tr tng trng nh 12.5% nm 2024 sau v hin ti vn tip tc ht ng.
  • Cc voucher bn c hu ht l bn cho client B2B vi phn ln l cc e-voucher loi Digital voucher 88% so vi Paper voucher, s lng voucher bn ra dng 'o' quy i thnh tin nhiu hn loi 'p' loi voucher quy i v sau cng l loi 'm' dng trn nhiu thng hiu trong cugf mt voucher.
  • Trong thi gian va qua, cng ty thu ht cc khch doanh nghip trn 12 lnh vc vi nhm doanh nghip ngn hng, bo him v FMCG l cc khch hng quan trng c s lng order nhiu nht.
  • Th trng min Nam c sc mua cao nht, cn tp trung pht trin hn.
  • Cng ty cng hp tc vi cc thng hiu ngng vi 9 phn loi kinh doanh cc san phm dch v trn h trng, ch yu l cc thng hiu offline nh nh hng, coffee & cake, supermarket v shopping tip cc thng hiu online nh tin ch v truyn thng.=> Voucher m thc v dch v thit yu c s dng nhiu nht.

C hi tng trng:

  • y mnh cc loi voucher linh hot (loi "o"), v y l loi c a chung nht.Khch hng a chung voucher c th quy i tin mt, cho thy h thch s linh hot trong vic mua sm thay v b gii hn mt sn phm c th. Voucher loi "m" t ph bin hn d kin. Doanh nghip c th y mnh loi ny bng cch m rng danh sch thng hiu chp nhn. C th ti u ha voucher loi "p" bng cch n gin ha iu kin s dng, thu ht thm ngi dng.
  • Tng cng th phn ti min Bc & Trung, ni c nhu cu thp hn.
  • Khai thc khch hng c nhn (C2C) m rng i tng ngi dng.
  • y mnh voucher trong ngnh cng ngh, ti chnh v nghin cu th trng, v y l nhm khch hng tim nng.

Lnh vc cn ci thin:

Gim t l voucher ht hn (10K n hng), c th thng qua nhc nh khch hng hoc ko di thi gian s dng. Tng cng a dng ha ngnh hng s dng voucher, c bit l nhm "Nh & Ph kin thi trang" (hin ti rt thp).

i su vo phn tch v nhm khch hng client, da vo data cho n thi im cui nm 2024, cc order c t t 35 khoch hng doanh nghip (trong c c 2 doanh nghip ngng hot ng trn h thng):

  • Quy m cc khch hng doanh nghip ch yu mc trung bnh v nh, cc khch hng doanh nghip quy m ln cn kh t. => Nn tm kim v y mnh tip cn nhng doanh nghip ln (Large Enterprise), vn c tim lc ti chnh v nhu cu tri n khch hng/nhn vin cao hn.
  • Cc doanh nghip ch yu s dng voucher Digital hn l Paper Voucher. => ch trng vic y bn cc Digital Voucher hn.
  • Doanh nghip la chn t hng voucher s dng cho cc danh mc trong ngnh F&B (m thc, c ph, tin ch) chim a s, cc ngnh v thi trang, mua sm, nh ca, y t cha c doanh thu ng k, cn tm cch m rng. => Voucher tin ch c s dng l do s tin li trong p dng ca n trong mua sm, cc voucher cc dnah mc v Heath Care, Flower, Fruit & Fesh Food, Supper Market & Shopping cn kh t c th l do gi tr ca voucher kh cao s
  • Nhn chng cc nhm khch hng u a chung loi voucher 'o' t bit l FMCG, Finance v Market Rearch; Bank u tin a chung c hai loi 'p' v 'o'. Insurance a chung c 3 nhng loi 'm' li c s dng nhiu.
  • Top 5 doanh nghip khch hng tim nng ng gp nhiu n t hng => Cn c cc u i duy tr v chin lc thu ht cc khch hng tim nng khc.

# Cu truy vn SQL
query = """
SELECT
    client_id,
    client_name,
    client_size,
    client_sector,
    client_type,
    client_location,
    AVG(value) AS avg_value,
    COUNT(DISTINCT order_id) AS order_count
FROM
    unified_data
GROUP BY
    client_id,
    client_name,
    client_size,
    client_sector,
    client_type,
    client_location
ORDER BY
    order_count DESC
LIMIT 5;
"""

# Thc hin truy vn v c d liu vo DataFrame
df = pd.read_sql(query, engine)

# Hin th kt qu
df

# Cu truy vn SQL
query = """
SELECT
    bc.name_en brand_category_name,
    ROUND(AVG(f.value), 2) AS avg_value,
    COUNT(DISTINCT f.order_id) order_count
FROM
    fact_voucher f
JOIN
    dim_brand b ON f.used_brand_id = b.brand_id
JOIN
    dim_category bc ON b.category_id = bc.category_id
GROUP BY
    bc.name_en
ORDER BY
    avg_value DESC
LIMIT 5;
"""

# Thc hin truy vn v c d liu vo DataFrame
df = pd.read_sql(query, engine)

Xt bin ng xu hng cho hot ng kinh doanh voucher trong khong thi 2022-2024 u 2025:

  • Xu hng t hng voucher ca cc doanh nghip khch hng nhiu vo giai on cui nm v thng 1 u nm (giai on mua sm chun b trc Tt, BlackFriday, dp lx Noel, ...) v gim vo thng 2 giai on Tt v sau Tt sau cc tng dn n cui nm.
  • Xu hng s dng voucher ca doanh nghip p dng quanh nm v cui nm s voucher cc doanh nghip s dng tng ln, i vi nm 2022 vic s dng tng dn phn nh mc s dng voucher ang c quan tm v p dng cc doanh nghip.
  • S lng voucher c to thm 2023 v 2024 t hn 2022 th hin khch hng a chung s dng cc sn phm voucher c, cng ty to c lng tin quay li ca khch hng. Xt xu hng s dng nhm thng hiu ca khch hng: Nhn thy xu hng chung l u s dng voucher cc nhm sn phm tin ch, F&B phn ln, tip n l truyn thng v Supermarket, shopping.

C hi tng trng & Ci thin

Nhn xt chung v xu hng

  • Xu hng ma v (cui nm & u nm) do nhu cu mua sm dp L, Tt, BlackFriday, .. v do nhu cu tng qu, tri n khch hng/nhn vin.
  • Xu hng s dng Digital Voucher v loi voucher link 'o' cc nhm thng hiu c la chn cao F&B (m thc, c ph, nh hng) v Tin ch (utilities) chim a s, do tnh thit yu v ph bin.
  • Doanh nghip khch hng lnh vc Bank, Insurance v FMCG vn ng vai tr quan trng. Cc lnh vc c tim nng pht trin l E-commerce, Entertainment v Supermarket & Shopping.
  • Th trng min Nam c sc mua ln nht, cc doanh nghip ch yu mua trc tip t Sales Team (Client B2B) giao dch thng qua trang thng mi in t cn t.
  • Phn khc khch hng theo quy m phn ln l doanh nghip va v nh (SME), doanh nghip ln cn t.

xut ci thin v c hi pht trin

  • S lng voucher mi gim nh 2023-2024 th hin khch hng a chung s dng li cc sn phm voucher c, cng ty to c lng tin khch hng quay li. => Tuy nhin, cn update cung cp a dng loi voucher mi hn ph hp vi th hiu th trng p ng nhu cu a dng phong ph cho ngi dng.
  • Tp trung pht trin cc sn phm cht lng v linh hot:
    • Tm kim i tc uy tn, xy dng voucher hp dn (gi tr va phi, chit khu tt), pt trin thm voucher online: Tch hp e-commerce, dch v streaming, game online theo kp xu hng tiu dng s.
    • Ch trng m rng thng hiu hp tc a dng cc danh mc (c bit l Tic ch, F&B v cc danh mc tim nng), m rng v v tr ca cc thng hiu m rng th trng ra c Bc v Trung.
    • Ch tm vo nhu cu s dng voucher ca ngi tiu dng to ra cc sn phm ph hp vi cc doanh nghip khch hng.
  • Chm sc khch hng lu nm v y mnh cc chin lc thu ht cc kjachs hng mi v tim nng khc.
  • Tn dng cc dp l dp l nh (Valentine, 8/3, 30/4 - 1/5) hay dp mua sm cui/ u/ gia thng chn hn dng voucher ph hpj duy tr sc mua.
